subtivals (1.8.0-10) stable; urgency=low

  * Switch to Qt5 on every platform (#266)
  * Forced ini format for settings (#268)
  * Basic support of DCP XML format (#207)
  * Support of Web live display (#252) 
  * Show basic introduction wizard for new users (#255)
  * Support of bold in simple text files using stars (#254)
  * Add bold and italic in style editor (#248)
  * The Hide desktop option is now safer, not stored in presets anymore (#241)
  * New column with comments (SSA, SRT, TXT) (#221, #235)
  * Option to show/hide milliseconds (#246)
  * Export printable spreadsheet for operators (#240)
  * Better apparence of unsaved presets (#262)
  * Fix advanced style popup position, now centered on main window (#259)
  * Fix default window position, not overlaping display screen anymore (#256)
  * Fix apparence of search button on OSX (#250)

